data.description: PRICE DROP!!!  Adorable down-to-the-studs renovation of this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in Central Tacoma! As you enter be greeted by light and bright open living room that flows to the dining area and gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances and island with seating. Slider door in kitchen leads to the large yard. Three spacious bedrooms, each with walk-in closets and ceiling fans. Ductless mini-splits with A/C to stay cool in the warmer months. Attached 1-car garage. Conveniently located just minutes to Tacoma Dome, shopping, highways, and much more!
